# `std.openapi` — OpenAPI metadata

```scalascript
// Marker consumed by the next route(...) registration.
// User-facing syntax is @openapi(...); the parser rewrites it to this call.
extern def openapi(
  summary: String = "",
  description: String = "",
  tags: List[String] = List(),
  deprecated: Boolean = false
): Unit
```
